            <div type="transcript" id="F167A">
                <lg type="stanza">
                    <l>I'm the little &quot;Heart's Ease&quot;!</l>
                    <l>I dont care for pouting skies!  </l>
                    <l>If the Butterfly delay </l>
                    <l>Can I, therefore, stay away?  </l>
                </lg>
                <lg type="stanza">
                    <l>If the Coward Bumble Bee</l>
                    <l>In his chimney corner stay, </l>
                    <l>I, must resoluter be!  </l>
                    <l>Who'll apologize for me?  </l>
                </lg>
                <lg type="stanza">
                    <l>Dear - Old fashioned, little flower!  </l>
                    <l>Eden is old fashioned, too!</l>
                    <l>Birds are antiquated fellows!  </l>
                    <l>Heaven does not change her blue.<app type="division"><lem><pb/></lem></app>
  </l>
                    <l>Nor will I, the little Heart's Ease - </l>
                    <l>Ever be induced to do!  </l>
                </lg>

            </div>     
